326
00:20:58.283 --> 00:20:59.980
Do you see my problem?

327
00:21:00.023 --> 00:21:02.417
Hmm.
Yeah, I think I see.

328
00:21:02.461 --> 00:21:03.940
Do you? Yeah.

329
00:21:03.984 --> 00:21:06.552
Is the problem that
