00:22:39.427 --> 00:22:41.386
"Hoping"?

362
00:22:41.429 --> 00:22:43.039
Praying.

363
00:22:44.258 --> 00:22:45.999
I prayed for my own safety.

364
00:22:46.042 --> 00:22:49.219
